IT WAS the stuff of nightmares, jagged teeth about to rip the life out of the lion keeper at a show in Doullens, northern France on Sunday afternoon.At the beginning of the Facebook video the lion is seen dragging the keeper on the floor with its jaws locked on his throat. As scared parents grab their children and run for safety, smoke is released into the arena to distract the lion and the keeper is freed from the lion.WATCH VIDEO HERE: